-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Third-party material
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Quotations and references to the following works are included for educational
purposes, with attribution, and remain the property of their respective rights
holders:

  * "Fundamentals of Co-Counseling Manual" and related Re-evaluation
    Counseling literature by Harvey Jackins and Rational Island Publishers.
    Vines of Life is not affiliated with the Re-evaluation Counseling
    Communities. Readers interested in the full tradition are encouraged to
    consult the authorized publications from Rational Island Publishers
    directly.

  * Scripture quotations are drawn from public-domain English translations
    (primarily the King James Version and the World English Bible).

If you are a rights holder of material referenced here and would like a
citation corrected, a quotation revised, or material removed, please open an
issue on this repository or contact Vines of Life.

